/.vs
/bin
/obj

# Personal AWS SSO reference files (see Config/README.md)
Config/config
Config/credentials

# Profile -> project key map (small, no PII by itself, but kept out of git
# for the same reason as the per-project data below).
Config/project-info.json

# Each project's own Project Info data, Wiki notes, and any file dropped in
# its "Dossier de fichiers" shortcut (contacts, network/VPN details,
# schemas...) -- contains PII, shared directly between colleagues instead
# of committed to git.
Config/ProjectFiles/

# Legacy global files from before Project Info/Wiki data moved into each
# project's own folder above; kept as migration backups on machines that
# still have one.
Config/wiki.json
Config/*.migrated-*

# Per-user Visual Studio project settings (machine-specific paths)
*.csproj.user
